	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, May 10th 8:53 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmm i am confused at exactaly WHAT bane spells are.. also on if its really worth is to haul my ass down to wherever i have to go to get ice commet. (i play on PVP and i am a dark)&nbsp;&nbsp;    thank yew<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
